"{\"uid\": \"rappler.com-sports-fencer-maxine-esteban-nervous-ready-debut-paris-olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  SUMMARY  This is AI generated summarization, which may have errors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999752983753298, \"rank\": 2.469927338609519e-05, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, always refer to the full article.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PROUD.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fencer Maxine Esteban wearing the Ivory Coast colors during the Paris Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 132, \"end\": 138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxine_Minniver\", \"score\": 0.9999962839629839, \"rank\": 3.694379545006421e-06, \"text\": \"Maxine\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxine_Minniver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxine_Minniver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MAXINE ESTEBAN FACEBOOK PAGE  MANILA, Philippines - Now \\\"100% ready\\\" for her Paris Games campaign, Filipino-Ivorian fencer Maxine Esteban still hopes to shake off the jitters on her Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxine_Minniver\", \"score\": 0.9999962839632113, \"rank\": 3.694379545006421e-06, \"text\": \"Maxine\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxine_Minniver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxine_Minniver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"More nervous because I know that I will be up against the world's best fencers - most of them seasoned Olympians - and the whole world will be watching,\\\" Esteban told Rappler.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The mental and emotional anxiety is real, but I have come this far, and in my maiden appearance, I am excited to do my best to make my supporters and family proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Esteban, who now represents Ivory Coast as anaturalized player, said \\\"everything\\\" in her Olympic buildup \\\"went as planned.\\\"\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But she admitted that she also had to learn to put aside the mental toll from her untimely exit from the Philippine fencing team.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is very hard,\\\" said Esteban.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Through the years, if there is anyone who has experienced the most setbacks and challenges, I think I would be one of them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just pray hard and try my best to cancel out the noise and to remember that as long as I do my best, I am good,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Esteban, the world No.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"27 in women's foil, opted toswitch nationalitiesfollowing a fallout with the Philippine fencing federation.\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that she already put all that behind, she just relishes the support from both Ivorians and Filipinos.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"score\": 0.9828895081170482, \"rank\": 0.017408245804481925, \"text\": \"Filipinos\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Both are simply amazing,\\\" said Esteban.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From the Ivory Coast, the support is phenomenal.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivory_Coast_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6355360300462163, \"rank\": 0.5615855175845418, \"text\": \"Ivory Coast\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivory_Coast_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivory_Coast_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ivorians have adopted me as one of their own, calling me a hero and their champ.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is really heartwarming.\\\"\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the Philippines, the support is equally heartwarming,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999349114813412, \"rank\": 6.358401407373292e-05, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is an overflow of well wishes and prayers.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really happy and honored to inspire the youth of both nations.\\\"\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Esteban, seeded 20th in the tournament, drew a first-round bye and will head straight to the round of 32 against France's Pauline Ranvier.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2057, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9805114737246136, \"rank\": 0.01729491395751632, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Ranvier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pauline Ranvier\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Ranvier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pauline_Ranvier\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samantha Catantan, the Philippines' first female fencer to qualify in the Olympics, will compete in the round of 64 against Brazils' Mariana Pistoia.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2107, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999349114813412, \"rank\": 6.358401407373292e-05, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistoia\", \"score\": 0.9999969326133147, \"rank\": 3.0642153943335543e-06, \"text\": \"Pistoia\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistoia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistoia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been training and competing all my life for this day,\\\" said Esteban.\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In terms of preparation, I would say 100%.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, being an elite athlete is a constant cycle of striving to improve, so in that aspect, we can never say we are 100% ready.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": []}]}"